reviews.review_text:
Hey Dan Helluva show here with just a little noise on the recording.

Dan, do you remember the road trip to Furthur Festival Reno 1996 we went to with mutual friends? We jammed at your pad in Frisco after. I just came across your tape list and noticed a Jerry show on it I went to that I would very much like to get from you if possible.

 barreramusic@gmail.com. Hope to hear from you (if you're the same D. C.).  Mark Barrera from Yosemite (from 1992-96 anyway).
